\id 1TI - Biblica® Open New Luo Translation 2020 
\h 1 Timotheo 
\toc1 Timotheo Mokwongo 
\toc2 1 Timotheo 
\toc3 1Tim 
\mt1 1 Timotheo 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 An Paulo jaote Kristo Yesu kaluwore gi Chik Nyasaye ma Jawarwa, kod Kristo Yesu, ma en genowa, 
\b  
\p  
\v 2 Andikoni in Timotheo wuoda mar adier kuom yie: 
\b  
\p Ngʼwono gi kech kod kwe moa kuom Nyasaye Wuoro gi Kristo Yesu Ruodhwa obed kodu. 
\b  
\s1 Siem kuom jopuonj mag miriambo 
\p  
\v 3 Kaka ne anyisi mondo itim kane an e wuodha madhiyo Makedonia, adwaro mondo imed bedo Efeso nikech jomoko ni kuno mapuonjo ji puonj mag miriambo manyaka ikwergi mondo giwe timo kamano.  
\v 4 Bende giwe keto chunygi e sigendini manono gi sigendini mag nonro mag anywola ma ok rum. Gik ma kamagi medo mana mbaka makelo miero kar gero tich Nyasaye, ma gerore kuom yie.  
\v 5 To wach maduongʼ mar Chikni en hera mawuok e chuny maler kendo maonge bura kod yie mar adier.  
\v 6 Jomoko osebaro oweyo magi mi gidonjo e mbekni mag oyuma maonge tiendgi.  
\v 7 Gigombo mondo gibed jopuonj Chik to gikia tiend gik ma giwacho kata gik ma giwuoyo kuomgi. 
\p  
\v 8 Wangʼeyo ni chik ber mana ka ngʼato konyore kode e yo mowinjore.  
\v 9 Wangʼeyo bende ni chik ok oket ni joma kare, to okete ni joketh chik gi jonjore; gi joma okia Nyasaye, kod joricho, gi joma timbegi ochido, kod joma odagi lemo; bende ni joma nego wuonegi kata minegi. Bende chikno oket ni jonek  
\v 10 gi jochode, kod chwo ma terore gi chwo wetegi gi joma timo ohand wasumbini gi jo-miriambo, kod joma kwongʼore kariambo chutho mondo gigweny adiera. Adier chik oket ne gimoro amora makedo gi puonj mar adier.  
\v 11 Puonjno owinjore kod Injili man-gi duongʼ mar Nyasaye mogwedhi, mane oket e lweta. 
\s1 Ngʼwono mar Ruoth kuom Paulo 
\p  
\v 12 Agoyo erokamano ni Kristo Yesu Ruodhwa mosemiya teko nikech ne okwana kaka ja-adiera mi oyiera e tichne.  
\v 13 Kata obedo ni chon ne awuoyo marach kuom Nyasaye kendo ne asando joma oyie ka akwiny, to nokecha nikech natimo gigo kuom kia kendo kuom bedo maonge yie.  
\v 14 Ngʼwono mar Ruodhwa ne ool kuoma mogundho, kaachiel gi yie kod hera mayudore kuom Kristo Yesu. 
\p  
\v 15 Wach mar adier mowinjore ji oyiego chuth en ni Kristo Yesu nobiro e piny mondo owar joricho, to an e jaricho marachie moloyo joricho duto.  
\v 16 To kuom mano Yesu Kristo nokecha an mane an jaricho ewi joricho duto, mondo onyis ngʼwonone maduongʼ maonge giko kuoma. Nodwaro mondo abed ranyisi, ne joma biro yie kuome mondo oyud ngima mochwere.  
\v 17 Opak Ruodhwa mochwere! En Ruoth ma ok tho, kendo ma ok ne. En e Nyasaye kende. Duongʼ kod pak odogne nyaka chiengʼ. Amin. 
\p  
\v 18 Timotheo wuoda, amiyi Chikni kaluwore gi weche mane okor kuomi chon. Ti kod chikni mondo iked lweny maber,  
\v 19 kisiko e yie motegno ka chunyi ok ngʼadni bura kaka jaketho. Jomoko osedagi winjo bura ma chunygi ngʼadonegi kuom gik maricho ma gitimo, omiyo koro yiegi osenimo.  
\v 20 Moko kuom jogo gin Humenayo gi Aleksanda, ma aseketo e lwet Satan mondo opuonjre ni kik giyany Nyasaye. 
\c 2  
\s1 Puonj kuom lemo 
\p  
\v 1 Wach mokwongo ma jiwo en ni ji duto mondo oter kwayogi e nyim Nyasaye ka gilamo kendo ka gigoyo erokamano ni Nyasaye  
\v 2 ne ruodhi gi joma nitie e loch duto mondo eka wadag gi kwe maonge tungni, ka waluoro Nyasaye kendo ka wan jomaler chuth.  
\v 3 Mani ber kendo moro Nyasaye Jawarwa,  
\v 4 madwaro ni ji duto oyud warruok kendo ongʼe adiera.  
\v 5 Nikech nitie Nyasaye achiel kende gi ngʼat achiel ma jathek e kind Nyasaye gi dhano, en e Kristo Yesu mane obiro e kido mar dhano.  
\v 6 Nochiwore owuon mondo ochul nengo mar waro ji duto. Kuom mano Nyasaye nokele kaka ranyisi e kinde mowinjore.  
\v 7 Mano emomiyo ne oyiera kaka jahul wach kendo kaka jaote. Awacho adier, ok ariambi, kendo an japuonj wach yie madier ne joma ok jo-Yahudi. 
\p  
\v 8 Emomiyo adwaro ni kamoro amora ma ji ochokoree ka lemo to chwo duto mondo otingʼ lwetgi maler malo ka gilemo, maonge mirima kata goyo mbaka.  
\v 9 Adwaro bende ni mon orwakre gi lewni mowinjore ka gibidhore kendo giritore maber, to rwakruokgi kik bed mana mar kado wich kata mar dhahabu kata mar rwako tigo ma nengone tek kata lewni ma nengogi tek,  
\v 10 to onego girwakre gi timbe mabeyo mowinjore gi mon mawacho ni oluoro Nyasaye. 
\p  
\v 11 Mon mondo opuonjre kolingʼ kendo koyie winjo wach.  
\v 12 Ok ayie mondo dhako opuonj ji kata obed gi teko ewi ngʼama dichwo; nyaka olingʼ mos,  
\v 13 nikech Adam ema nokwong chwe eka bangʼe Hawa.  
\v 14 To bende Adam ok ema ne owuondi, to dhako ema ne owuondi, mi odoko jaketho.  
\v 15 Kata kamano mon noyud resruok e yor nywolo nyithindo, ka gisiko e yie kod hera gi ngima maler kendo modimbore. 
\c 3  
\p  
\v 1 Ma en wach mar adiera ni ka ngʼato oketo chunye mondo obed jatend kanisa to odwaro tich mogen.  
\v 2 Jatend kanyakla mar jo-Kristo nyaka bed ngʼat ma wach moro amora marach onge kuome, chwor dhako achiel kende, ngʼat mobidhore, moritore, kendo modimbore, ngʼat moluor, mohero rwako welo kendo japuonj molony,  
\v 3 ngʼat ma ok ohero kongʼo, ngʼat ma ok ger, bende owinjore obed ngʼat mamuol, ma ok ohero dhawo kendo ma ok ohero pesa.  
\v 4 Nyaka obed ngʼat morito ode maber kendo nyaka one ni nyithinde winjo wachne gi luor mowinjore.  
\v 5 (To ka ngʼato ok nyal rito ode owuon, to ere kaka dorit kanisa Nyasaye?)  
\v 6 Kik obed ngʼat moyudo warruok machiegni, nono to sunga nyalo make mi opodhi kendo bura loye kaka noloyo jachien.  
\v 7 Bende nyaka obed ngʼat ma joma ok oyie wuoyo kuome maber, mondo kik obadho mar jachien gaje mi opodhi kendo one wichkuot. 
\p  
\v 8 Kamano bende jokony e kanisa bende nyaka bed joma imiyo luor, joma odimbore, joma ok madh kongʼo kendo joma ok oowre gi yudo ohala e yo ma ok nikare.  
\v 9 Nyaka gimak adiera matut mar yie gi chuny maler maonge richo moro amora.  
\v 10 Nyaka temgi mokwongo, to ka oyud ni onge wach moro marach kuomgi eka mondo yienegi bedo jokony. 
\p  
\v 11 Kamano bende, mondgi nyaka bed joma owinjore mi luor, kik gibed mon mohero kuoth, to owinjore gibed mon moritore kendo ma jo-adiera e weche duto. 
\p  
\v 12 Jakony kanisa nyaka bed ngʼatno man-gi dhako achiel kende kendo mopuonjo nyithinde gi joode duto maber.  
\v 13 Joma osetiyo maber yudo nying maber kendo gibedo gi chir e yie margi kuom Kristo Yesu. 
\p  
\v 14 Kata obedo ni ageno biro iri mapiyo to andikoni wechegi mag puonj mondo;  
\v 15 kaponi adeko to ingʼe kaka ji onego owuothi e dier kanyakla mar jo-Nyasaye, ma en kanisa mar Nyasaye mangima, ma en e siro kendo mise mar adiera.  
\v 16 Chutho, mano kaka weche Nyasaye odhiero ngʼeyo kendo nigi duongʼ miwuoro: 
\q1 Kristo nobiro e ringruok, 
\q2 kendo Roho nonyiso ratiro ni oonge ketho, 
\q1 malaike ne onene, 
\q2 kendo wachne ne oyal e kind ogendini, 
\q1 ji ne oyie kuome e piny ngima, 
\q2 kendo ne otere malo e duongʼ mar Nyasaye. 
\c 4  
\s1 Puonj ma omi Timotheo 
\p  
\v 1 Roho Maler wacho ni e ndalo giko jomoko nowe yie mi giluw weche chunje mawuondo ji kod puonj mayoreyore mag jochiende.  
\v 2 Puonj ma kamago aa kuom jo-miriambo mawuondore, jogo ma pachgi manyiso ni gin joketho osetho mana ka gima orew gi nyinyo maliet.  
\v 3 Gitamo ji mondo kik okendre, kendo gisiemogi mondo kik gicham chiemo mamoko ma Nyasaye ochiwo mondo joma oyie kendo mongʼeyo adiera okaw gi erokamano.  
\v 4 Nikech gik moko duto ma Nyasaye ochweyo beyo, kendo ok owinjore wakwer chiemo moro amora ka wachame gi erokamano,  
\v 5 nikech osepwodhe maler gi wach Nyasaye kod lamo. 
\p  
\v 6 Ka ipuonjo Jowete wechegi to ibiro bedo jatich maber mar Kristo Yesu, ka idongori e adiera mar yie gi puonj mabeyo miseluwo.  
\v 7 Bed mabor chuth gi sigendini manono mag piny maonge tiende to moloyo tiegri ibed molony e luoro Nyasaye.  
\v 8 Nikech kata obedo ni tuke mag rieyo del konyo ji e yore moko, to luoro Nyasaye nigi gweth mathoth moloyo, en gi ohala e ngima masani kendo e ngima mabiro bende. 
\p  
\v 9 Ma en wach madiera mowinjore ji oyiego chuth,  
\v 10 nikech mano emomiyo watiyo matek kendo wakedo, ka waketo genowa kuom Nyasaye mangima, ma en Jawar mar ji duto, to moloyo en Jawar joma oyie. 
\p  
\v 11 Chik ji ka ipuonjogi wechegi.  
\v 12 Kik iyie mondo ngʼato ochayi nikech pod itin, to bed ranyisi ni joma oyie kuom weche miwacho, gi gik mitimo, kod hera miherogo ji kendo kuom bedo ja-adiera kendo kuom dak e ngima maler.  
\v 13 Ket chunyi kuom somo Ndiko ne ji e lela, kendo kuom jiwo ji kendo puonjo ji nyaka chopi abi.  
\v 14 Kik ijwangʼ michni mane omiyi kaka nokor kuomi chiengʼ mane jodongo oketo lwetgi kuomi. 
\p  
\v 15 Tim gigi gi chunyi duto, kichiwori chuth mar neno ni gitimore mondo ji duto one kaka imedo dhi nyime maber e yore duto.  
\v 16 Rit ngimani gi weche mipuonjo maber. Tim kinda kodgi mak iweyogi, nikech ka itimo kamano eka inires ngimani iwuon kaachiel gi ngima joma winjo weche mipuonjo. 
\c 5  
\s1 Puonj kuom mon ma chwogi otho, jodongo gi wasumbini 
\p  
\v 1 Kik idhaw gi ngʼama duongʼ gi dwol makwiny, to wuo kode mamuol giluor mana ka wuonu monywoli. Kaw yawuowi matindo ka oweteni,  
\v 2 to mon madongo kaw ka mineni, kendo mon matindo kaw ka nyimineni, e yo maler chutho. 
\p  
\v 3 Nyaka ipar mon ma chwogi otho modongʼ kendgi madwaro kony e yor adiera.  
\v 4 To ka dhako ma chwore otho moro nigi nyithindo kata nyikwayo to ber mondo gitingʼ nying Nyasaye malo kuom rito joodgi ka gikonyo jonywolgi gi kweregi kod deyegi, nikech timo kamano longʼo ni Nyasaye.  
\v 5 Dhako ma chwore otho keto genone duto kuom Nyasaye, kendo osiko olamo odiechiengʼ gotieno kokwayo Nyasaye mondo okonye.  
\v 6 To dhako ma chwore otho mohero mor mar piny, osetho kata obedo ni pod ongima.  
\v 7 Puonj ji wechegi bende, mondo kik ngʼato obed gi bura.  
\v 8 Ka ngʼato ok orito wedene, to moloyo ka ok orito joode owuon, to osekwedo yie marwa, kendo orach moloyo japiny. 
\p  
\v 9 Dhako moro amora ma chwore otho ok nyal ndik nyinge kama indike nying mon ma chwogi otho ka hikgi ok oloyo higni piero auchiel, to bende nyaka bed ni ne osebedo ja-adiera e dakne gi chwore,  
\v 10 kendo ongʼeye kuom timbene mabeyo kaka oserito nyithindo e yo mowinjore kendo osebedo kohero rwako welo e ode, kendo osebedo ka olwoko tiend jomaler kendo ka okonyo joma ni e chandruok, kochiwore chuth ni timo gik mabeyo duto. 
\p  
\v 11 Kik iyie mondo mon ma chwogi otho ma pod tindo ndik nying-gi kama indikoe nying mon ma chwogi otho. Nikech ka ringregi ohewogi gi gombo to giweyo Kristo ka gimanyo chwo mondo okendgi.  
\v 12 Kuom mano gikelo kum kuomgi giwegi, nikech giseketho singruokgi mokwongo.  
\v 13 To bende ewi mano, gibedo jo-samuoyo ma budho abudha, ka gibayo abaya e ute ji koni gi koni. Ok gibed mana jo-samuoyo ma budho abudha kende, to bende gibedo jokuoth ka gichuogore e weche ji mamoko kendo ka giwuoyo e weche ma ok onego giwuoye.  
\v 14 Kuom mano daher mondo mon ma chwogi otho matindo okendi, mondo ginywol nyithindo, kendo girit utegi mondo kik gimi jasigu thuolo mar ketho nying joma oyie.  
\v 15 Chutho, moko odok chien mi koro giluwo Satan. 
\p  
\v 16 To ka ngʼama oyie moro odak gi mon ma chwogi otho e dalane, onego okonygi en owuon mondo kik kanisa bed gi tingʼ mapek mar ritogi, eka kanisa okony mon ma chwogi otho mamoko man kendgi chuth maonge ngʼama nyalo konyogi. 
\p  
\v 17 Jodong kanisa morito weche mag kanisa onego yud pok margi nyadiriyo, to moloyo jodongo ma tichgi en yalo kod puonjo wach Nyasaye.  
\v 18 Nimar Ndiko owacho niya, “Kik utwe dho dhiangʼ kaywayo lodi ma idinogo cham,”\f + \fr 5:18 \ft \xt Rap 25:4\f* kendo niya, “Jatich ber gi chudo kuom tije motiyo.”\f + \fr 5:18 \ft \xt Luk 10:7\f* 
\v 19 Kik iyie gi ketho modonjnego jaduongʼ kanisa kaonge joneno ariyo kata adek.  
\v 20 Joma osiko timo richo nyaka kwer ratiro e nyim ji eka joma moko obed maluor.  
\v 21 Achiki e nyim Nyasaye kendo e nyim Kristo Yesu, kaachiel gi malaika moyier, ni mondo ilu puonjgi adimba ma ok idewo wangʼ ngʼato kendo ma ok idok kor ngʼato angʼata. 
\p  
\v 22 Kik irikni yieyo lwedo kuom ji, kendo kik iriwri e richo ji mamoko. Ritri mondo ngimani osik kaler. 
\p  
\v 23 Ok onego imodh pi kende, to madh divai matin mondo okonyni iyi nikech midekre ma in-go pile. 
\p  
\v 24 Jomoko richogi ongʼongʼore kendo otelo nyimgi ka terogi e bura to richo jomoko to opondo kendo luwo bangʼ-gi.  
\v 25 Mano bende e kaka tim ngʼato makare bende ongʼongʼore, kendo kata mana mago motimo mopondo fwenyore bangʼe. 
\c 6  
\p  
\v 1 Ji duto manie tich mar misumba onego omi jotendgi luor mowinjore kodgi mondo nying Nyasaye kod puonj mwapuonjo kik yany.  
\v 2 Jogo man-gi ruodhi moyie kuom Kristo kik nyisgi achaya moro amora nikech gin jowete kuom Kristo. Kar timo kamano to owinjore gitinegi maber moloyo, nikech jogo mayudo ohala e tichgi gin owete kuom Kristo ma gihero. 
\s1 Jopuonj mag miriambo kod hero pesa 
\p Magi e gik manyaka ipuonj ji kijiwogi matek.  
\v 3 Ka ngʼato opuonjo gima opogore ma ok owinjore gi puonj ma adier mag Ruodhwa Yesu Kristo kendo mamiyo ji luoro Nyasaye,  
\v 4 to ngʼeuru ni ngʼat ma kamano wuondore kende owuon bende onge gima ongʼeyo. Ngʼat ma kamano kasore gi mino wach kendo gigoyo mbaka manono makelo nyiego, gi dhawo, gi kuoth, kod chich maricho;  
\v 5 kod miero ma ok rum e kind joma pachgi osekethore kendo ma adiera oselalnigi. Giparo ni lamo Nyasaye en yor yudo mwandu. 
\p  
\v 6 To geno Nyasaye gi chuny modhil en ohala maduongʼ.  
\v 7 Nimar onge gima ne wakelo e pinyni kendo onge gima wabiro kawo wadhigo.  
\v 8 Omiyo ka wan gi chiemo kod lewni to mago mondo oromwa.  
\v 9 Joma gombo mondo obed gi mwandu nwangʼo tem kendo gimoko e obadho kuom gik mofuwo mangʼeny kod gombo mathoth kendo gombo ma kamano kelo kethruok kendo miyo ji lal.  
\v 10 Nikech hero pesa e chakruok mar kit richo duto. Jomoko ma chunygi osegedo e yore mag yudo pesa oseweyo yie mi gichwowo chunygi giwegi gi masiche mathoth. 
\s1 Paulo ojiwo Timotheo 
\p  
\v 11 To in, ngʼat Nyasaye, pogri gi mago duto kiketo chunyi kuom ngima makare kod luoro Nyasaye gi yie kod hera kendo kitimo kinda kod muolo.  
\v 12 Ked lweny maber mar yie, kendo mak matek wach ngima mochwere mane oluongine chiengʼ mane itimo neno maber e nyim joneno mathoth.  
\v 13 E nyim Nyasaye mamiyo gik moko duto ngima, kendo e nyim Kristo Yesu ma notimo neno maber kane owuoyo e nyim Pontio Pilato, achiki ni  
\v 14 mondo irit Chikni ma ok iketho bende ma ok irem nyaka chop Ruodhwa Yesu Kristo fwenyre  
\v 15 ma Nyasaye nokel e kinde mochano owuon; Nyasaye mipako, ma en wuon Loch makende, kendo ma en Jaloch mar joloch kendo Ruoth mar ruodhi;  
\v 16 Jal ma ok tho kendo modak e ler ma dhano ok nyal ngʼiyo tir; kendo Jal maonge ngʼama oseneno kata manyalo neno. Duongʼ gi loch duto odogne nyaka chiengʼ. Amin. 
\p  
\v 17 Nyis joma nigi mwandu e pinyni mondo kik gibed jongʼayi bende kik giket genogi kuom mwandu mabiro leny nono to giket genogi kuom Nyasaye mamiyowa gik moko duto mabup mondo wabedgo mamor.  
\v 18 Chikgi mondo gitim maber, ka gipongʼ gi mwandu mag timbe mabeyo kendo gibed mangʼwon ka giikore pogo mwandugi ne ji mochando gik ma gin-go.  
\v 19 Ka gitimo kamano to gibiro kano mwandu ne gin giwegi, kendo mano nodognegi mise motegno e ndalo mabiro, mondo omi gibed gi ngima madiera man-gi tiende. 
\p  
\v 20 To in Timotheo, rit maber gima oseketi e lweti maber mondo iriti. Pogri gi mbekni manono mag piny gi gwenyo wach ma ji okawo ni rieko to ok gin rieko.  
\v 21 Jomoko mawacho ni gin gi rieko ma kamano osebayo yo moweyo yie. 
\b  
\b  
\p Ngʼwono obed kodu un duto.